BT /F1 10 Tf 42 790 Td 14 TL (# Jay Ambe PG Live Server + MySQL Setup Guide) Tj T* () Tj T* (## Required Stack) Tj T* () Tj T* (- Node.js) Tj T* (- React) Tj T* (- MySQL 8+) Tj T* (- Bootstrap) Tj T* (- Tailwind CSS) Tj T* () Tj T* (## Frontend Build) Tj T* () Tj T* (1. Open terminal in `payingguest`.) Tj T* (2. Install dependencies:) Tj T* (   `npm install`) Tj T* (3. Build React:) Tj T* (   `npm run build`) Tj T* (4. Upload the `build` folder to your live hosting panel or serve it using Node/Nginx/Apache.) Tj T* () Tj T* (## MySQL Setup) Tj T* () Tj T* (1. Create a MySQL database on the live server.) Tj T* (2. Recommended database name: `jay_ambe_pg`.) Tj T* (3. Import this SQL file:) Tj T* (   `database/mysql/jay_ambe_pg_schema.sql`) Tj T* (4. Confirm these important tables exist:) Tj T* (   `students`, `admissions`, `buildings`, `floors`, `rooms`, `room_items`, `allocations`,) Tj T* (`payments`, `expenses`, `inquiries`, `support_tickets`, `invoices`, `calendar_events`,) Tj T* (`staff`, `roles`, `admins`.) Tj T* () Tj T* (## Environment Variables) Tj T* () Tj T* (Create `.env` from `.env.example`.) Tj T* () Tj T* (Required values:) Tj T* () Tj T* (- `REACT_APP_API_BASE_URL`) Tj T* (- `MYSQL_HOST`) Tj T* (- `MYSQL_PORT`) Tj T* (- `MYSQL_DATABASE`) Tj T* (- `MYSQL_USER`) Tj T* (- `MYSQL_PASSWORD`) Tj T* () Tj T* (Optional payment/message values:) Tj T* () Tj T* ET
